	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />is there any way to play famicom disk system on an NES system? Obviously, due to the shape of the RAM adapter, it won't physically fit into the NES even with an import adapter, and I really don't feel comfortable with having the lid on the NES off. I have an RGB NES so getting a famicom just for FDS really isn't an option (I personally have no idea where to get an RGB modded famicom, even if it were possible)
<br />
<br />any ideas are appreciated!

		

		</td>
	</tr>
